<plot>Kay Gonda--the greatest movie star and celebrity of the 1930s--is accused of murder. On the run from the police, she seeks refuge at the homes of her most passionate fans--six men who have pledged their love to her through their letters. Actually innocent of the crime, she is really on a quest to find one man of integrity among them--one man who will not betray her. Only this can rekindle her hope in mankind and her desire to remain a movie idol.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?256233</url></doc>
